Inferno yelled as he was blown apart. He yelled as he was blasted 
down the hall way and lost an arm and a leg. He was blown through the 
wall as if fired out of a cannon then skidded across the ground 
"B-Beast mode" he magaged to get out, although even in his ant mode 
he only had two legs left. He slumped to the ground waiting till he 
could move again and hoped that maximals would pass him off as some 
insect when they got back.
